{"tid":2089084,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"國安幾時來香港，所有香港公務員公職人員，宣誓沒有BNO及英國戶籍，否則勾結外國勢力啊嚴重違反國安法","createTime":"2020-07-01T13:19:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-03T07:55:32.000Z","uid":34877,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f4e60f8e285a5b70d6c1a1a8d4084cafab07cb39","tid":2089084,"uid":34877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T13:19:00.000Z","msg":"中國不容許勾結外國勢力，由政府人員做起"},{"pid":"95c60c6cfaa017bc56f8d84ad83469c67594c528","tid":2089084,"uid":34877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T13:19:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3ea941ef9c7a2c59d59cf150ea2a8b36abca1ba","tid":2089084,"uid":34877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T13:20:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78b463ac54128ee2cd951606dedb6b85490e654f","tid":2089084,"uid":107023,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T13:21:04.000Z","msg":"其實呢個做法合理<br />\n公職人員必需愛國，點可以有外國護照"},{"pid":"7fb6e1a83bd7e6cef05e5dd2c94f13964b0654ad","tid":2089084,"uid":5289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T13:21:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"548910c81610cc7bc414967d330191e4cb104b07","tid":2089084,"uid":229508,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T13:21:34.000Z","msg":"全部政府部門都不得有外籍"},{"pid":"da6a5e275da18eda4027e76895044f2095771b51","tid":2089084,"uid":22700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T13:22:30.000Z","msg":"玩大D  連支那都唔敢咁做"},{"pid":"d4a897fd647540c50669a62955adb5738d3cf0d6","tid":2089084,"uid":104371,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T13:23:58.000Z","msg":"絕對認同<br />\n要記住國家出糧俾你<br />\n唔該要忠於國家"},{"pid":"f76026f62bfa5618b9cc35c2676be364d25c140a","tid":2089084,"uid":34877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T14:03:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e04a27ef54930c13b9db2de1d4de43b897c46075","tid":2089084,"uid":34877,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T16:17:58.000Z","msg":"香港警察是維護國安法最前線，要求其本人及其家屬不得持有BNO及其他國籍"},{"pid":"e0744cf10be3ae98ba6b48bdf772bdad3dba4f4c","tid":2089084,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T16:44:30.000Z","msg":"借個位，BNO平權正視聽<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黑色五毛分化警告，大量五毛正在用藍絲有BNO、走人對唔住97後割97後等風向進行分化</span></span></strong>，大家小心。<br />\n<br />\n1.<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家比人拉過/有小朋友（細路是重點，香港未來棟樑，正如今時今日d前線義士，咪比佢地洗腦變小糞紅，否則香港係真正玩完）的話就應該即刻走</span></span></strong>，其他人亦應該起碼做好隨時走既準備，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">香港抗爭運動已經由本土抗爭升級為準國際戰爭， 我們能做的十分有限。 相反大家離開或準備好隨時可以離開，則美國及其盟友可以隨時採取行動，對香港進行制裁，令香港達至零經濟活動，攬炒香港經濟， 甚至日後作出軍事行動亦無需擔心誤傷香港人。</span></span></strong> 而且大家亦可用移民理由提取所有資產及強積金進一步<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">打擊香港的財政儲備</span></span></strong>。<br />\n而且多人走亦可以起到掩護最需要走既手足，救奶左野手足係目前最重要既事。<br />\n<br />\n2.大家<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無需擔心藍絲以及黑警移民英國</span></span></strong>，藍絲得兩種a.垃圾b.收成期，a.涯唔到六年移民監b.揾錢唔捨得走/走要承受巨大損失<br />\n<br />\n重點：大家<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不應該反對平權或推到現階段設立篩選，因為這樣會妨礙奶左野手足逃難</span></span></strong>。反而，大家應該在藍絲移民英國後再篤灰。大家，要記住，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">篤灰係一把藍絲頭上既利劍，一日未入籍一日都嚮度，我就係要佢地嚮英國每一日都擔心比人篤灰，呢樣恐懼做為懲罰先係最大懲罰</span></span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n3.<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">97後手足唔會被割</span></span></strong>，首先，佢地可以跟BNO父母及配偶前往英國。第二，對於<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">未受BNO平權保障嘅人佢哋仲有美國既救生艇計劃</span></span></strong>，該計劃估計幾日內亦會通過。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">希望樓主可以pin，一齊擊退五毛</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"8af2ce63e7d08d513b87ea5bca9350bcb68d36ff","tid":2089084,"uid":34877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T19:36:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2f7e6509372fed61b731661926bd5990b3e0709","tid":2089084,"uid":288304,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T19:43:19.000Z","msg":"支持国安法，應該炒晒持有BNO同其他外國護照的公務員，退咗休的應該cut甚至歸還 長俸"},{"pid":"679a0f6fea7eb77d70a6cd93dd1d50a369039601","tid":2089084,"uid":34877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T07:24:14.000Z","msg":"邊度可以直接向中央政府舉報"},{"pid":"e5f5a08b02172e0b220337a3fdd228ceff03d2ad","tid":2089084,"uid":34877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T07:36:26.000Z","msg":"今日話有消息政府會咁做，作為愛黨愛國的一定要支持，否則顛覆國家政權嚴重違反國安法"},{"pid":"d66dcab929ec146200e4baa3a164fbed9282501f","tid":2089084,"uid":34877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T07:55:32.000Z","msg":"原來ann姐有睇🥰"}]}